Package: kbodatamining
Type: Package
Title: Kbo Data Mining and Analysis with R
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-01-31
Authors@R: person("Sunsick", "Choo", email = "1993ss@naver.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package analyzes records such as AVG and ERA through Korean baseball data.
              And The analyzed records are shown in a box score. 
              The functions in this package draw a plot that compares players or teams based on a box score.
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10)
